➜宁波文化广场朗豪酒店：明阁携手马爹利焕新主厨餐桌
http://www.sohu.com/a/421628052_100116241	17856
<p>金秋送爽，硕果飘香，明阁携手马爹利焕新主厨餐桌，大厨即席献技，近距离为宾客烹饪美馔珍馐，搭配马爹利干邑，打造舌尖上的经典。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200929/95776941040f447cafe3226cc50ba0a8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200929/420b86d57c934bb694f00544e2fc39c6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200929/6bf37340d41f41df83bbd505b9b969f6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
